commit.message: Disabled etag header sent by nodejs, misc. refactors
New grounds-up implementation of the backend. It does away with the Router because it's overkill, frankly. Also solves the backend-daemon communication problems
Refactored to use c++ threads instead of pthread, fixed busy-wait while(1) loop at the end (replaced with pthread_exit on main thread)
modified listener to print to stdout
more operations, pause, resume and kill
when the feature man throws in a little extra
